Lockout Policy	This security feature activates when a user enters an incorrect password multiple times. It temporarily locks the account to prevent unauthorized access.	5 times
Data Sync	Controls the frequency at which field devices (e.g., sensors, SCADA units) synchronize with the central system for monitoring and analysis.	1 week
